
<div class="mt-5">

<% if params[:emailid] %>


<div class="card" style="width: 25rem;">
  <div class="card-body">
    <h5 class="card-title">Reset your Blood Requestor password</h5>
    <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">BloodHub password reset</h6>
    <p class="card-text">
<h3>BloodHub password reset</h3>
 
We heard that you lost your BloodHub password. Sorry about that!

But don’t worry! You can use the following button to reset your password:
<%= link_to 'Reset Password', forgot_password_path(:emailid=>params[:emailid],:token=>params[:token])  ,class:"btn btn-success my-2 my-sm-0 mr-1" %></p>
    
    <p>If you don’t use this link within 3 hours, it will expire.</p>
    Thanks,<br>
The BloodHub Team <br>
    
  </div>
</div>


<% else %>


<% end %>
</div>

